08/08/2003
BELGRADE, Serbia-Montenegro -- Former Federal President and head of the Democratic Party of Serbia (DSS) Vojislav Kostunica said Thursday (7 August) that a draft declaration on Kosovo would be prepared next week. 
He also said the draft would be considered at the very first session of the Serbian Parliament in the autumn. 
Kostunica said the document would include the positions of DSS and the Serbian government and would follow the guidelines prescribed by Nebojsa Covic, Belgrade's co-ordinator on Kosovo. 
(B92, BBC, Beta - 07/08/03)
